data.address: State Road 405 Between Range Road And Ea, Cape Canaveral, FL 32920
data.details: Get ready for a night of excitement and exploration at the Scout Overnight Adventure. Scouts get nose-to-nose with Space Shuttle Atlantis, meet a veteran NASA astronaut and solve the Great Rocket Scavenger Hunt, led by our Overnight Adventure instructor team. This event costs $125 per girl and $105 per adult.
